    <label>6B43 body armor (black)</label>
    <description>The 6B43 bulletproof vest of 6A protection class (roughly equivalent to class IIIA) is designed for protection from light weapons bullets - including BP and PP - fragments of grenades, mines, and melee weapons, as well as reducing the risk of after-penetration effects during combat situations.
	
